132
0:06:34.33,000 --> 0:06:36,000
there are a lot of linkages --

133
0:06:36.33,000 --> 0:06:38,000
120, as a matter of fact,

134
0:06:38.33,000 --> 0:06:4,000
if you remember your factorials.

135
0:06:40.33,000 --> 0:06:42,000
