139
0:06:49.33,000 --> 0:06:51,000
Suppose we double the number of influencers

140
0:06:51.33,000 --> 0:06:53,000
from five to 10.

141
0:06:53.33,000 --> 0:06:57,000
Does that mean we've doubled the number of pieces of information

142
0:06:57.33,000 --> 0:06:59,000
