147
0:07:09.33,000 --> 0:07:12,000
But computers,

148
0:07:12.33,000 --> 0:07:15,000
they can. They don't need coffee breaks,

149
0:07:15.33,000 --> 0:07:18,000
they don't need vacations,

150
0:07:18.33,000 --> 0:07:2,000
they don't need to go to sleep at night,

151
0:07:20.33,000 --> 0:07:23,000
they don't ask for raises either.

152
0:07:23.33,000 --> 0:07:25,000
They can keep this information straight

153
0:07:25.33,000 --> 0:07:28,000
and that means that we can process the information.

154
0:07:28.33,000 --> 0:07:3,000
