163
0:07:51.33,000 --> 0:07:54,000
is right in predicting things whose outcome is not yet known,

164
0:07:54.33,000 --> 0:07:58,000
when the experts who provided the data inputs

165
0:07:58.33,000 --> 0:08:,000
